fields.Microsoft.VSTS.TCM.ReproSteps:
1. Create a engagement
  2. Setup MA, PAP
  3. Generate a TOD.
  4. Open the TOD generate a Sample Selection table
  5. Make some change to trigger the Top up  modal, then click button Top up
  6. Make some change again, then click the Update samples/selections table button to trigger the subsequent instance Top up modal.
  7. Click button Cancel in subsequent instance Top up modal
  8. Try to click button Cancel
fields.Custom.ActualResult:
Nothing happen when user click button Update samples/selections table button
Please see my attachment for more details.
fields.Custom.ExpectedResult: User should available to trigger Update samples/selections table button again.
